19:01.256 --> 19:01.896
Just Google it.

19:01.916 --> 19:02.797
Google it when you get home.

19:03.298 --> 19:04.960
It's a whole thing, teenagers.

19:05.040 --> 19:11.447
Anyway, you got to stay away from the people that are going to take you in the wrong direction.

19:11.487 --> 19:23.900
You got to get with people and surround yourself with people that are going to support you and point you towards God and give you that emotional spiritual and the psychological support that you need as you go through the holidays with the empty chairs.

19:23.920 --> 19:24.561
Does that make sense?

19:25.462 --> 19:27.804
