23:13.730 --> 23:17.856
to be with us, didn't the prophet Isaiah say in Isaiah 17?

23:18.077 --> 23:32.719
Isaiah 7 verse 14, that they'll be assigned, the virgin will be pregnant, and she'll give birth to a child, and you were to call his name Immanuel, and that means God with us.

23:33.620 --> 23:34.802
