23:35.303 --> 23:37.586
Like how is it that God comforts you and I?

23:37.666 --> 23:42.932
Yes, He sends people into our life, the right people, but He also sends His presence.

23:43.113 --> 23:44.454
He takes the initiative.

23:44.955 --> 23:46.577
The Virgin will give birth to a baby.

23:46.777 --> 23:48.539
Christ will come when He rises.

23:48.559 --> 23:52.164
He will send the Spirit and the Spirit will indwell us and He will be our comforter.

23:54.847 --> 23:58.832
