27:55.829 --> 27:57.011
Fill them with your spirit.

27:58.112 --> 28:02.738
Assure them that it's gonna be okay and that you're with them.

28:05.698 --> 28:06.219
We love you.

28:06.800 --> 28:08.522
We pray this in the precious name of Jesus.

28:09.684 --> 28:12.228
Amen.

28:12.248 --> 28:14.011
