32:12.994 --> 32:19.643
Experience your joy, peace, and comfort.

32:21.346 --> 32:27.474
So right now, I ask you to fill my heart with your spirit.

32:28.194 --> 32:39.491
the pericletos, the comforter, and comfort me in my struggles, in my pain, and in my loss.

32:41.915 --> 32:57.298
And from this day forward, lead me, guide me, teach me to trust you, to obey you, to honor you, and to love you.

32:58.850 --> 33:00.253
It's in Jesus' name I pray.

33:01.375 --> 33:01.696
Amen.

33:03.479 --> 33:05.523
Can we give God glory today to our today, amen.

33:05.964 --> 33:06.365
Amen.

